{"tid":252144,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - XO醬青椒炒鮮魷","createTime":"2017-05-21T13:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T14:46:03.000Z","uid":74981,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"040fdb0d894260fa0c9be9797c724ff1819edb54","tid":252144,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/194bf648a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2F194bf648a2.jpg&h=34645992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f3d90Jfhf28\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ff3d90Jfhf28&d=orEqo2PDfTnkAfc6t3i5rp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c5a9375e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f3d90Jfhf28</a><br />\n<br />\n材料:<br />\n<br />\n鮮魷1隻切件<br />\n<br />\n青椒1個切件<br />\n<br />\n蒜蓉2茶匙<br />\n<br />\n辣椒2隻切碎<br />\n<br />\nXO醬1湯匙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 鮮魷稍為出水撈起備用, 等炒果陣唔好係咁出水<br />\n<br />\n2. 起油獲,慢火爆蒜蓉, 辣椒, XO醬.<br />\n<br />\n3.落青椒開中火爆<br />\n<br />\n4. 炒到咁上下落鮮魷, 開大火快炒, 完成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6f943ccc01aa384d9d407e6a58c68c6d0c04c2","tid":252144,"uid":39317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想食"},{"pid":"f87806bd05a019344fbf8b1398a17db9efcfccac","tid":252144,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想食</blockquote><br />\n哩個簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb01bc2b2637f25df435dff1a8bf21ff7f54d35","tid":252144,"uid":38923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoj